00:34:24.400 --> 00:34:26.429
and he's having heart disease.

00:34:26.429 --> 00:34:32.159
So my question is, how are your
diets mapping to Indian food?

00:34:32.159 --> 00:34:35.550
Because food, as you said,
is a major part of the plan.

00:34:35.550 --> 00:34:37.489
But if the food is--

00:34:37.489 --> 00:34:40.800
so Indian food is typically
pretty [INAUDIBLE]..

00:34:40.800 --> 00:34:43.199
But if we move into a
different kind of diet,

00:34:43.199 --> 00:34:46.494
then he will not like it and
he'll probably reject it.

00:34:46.494 --> 00:34:47.396
