00:36:52.020 --> 00:36:54.300
more than being healthy,
whether you're six or 60,

00:36:54.300 --> 00:36:56.250
people want to feel
free and in control.

00:36:56.250 --> 00:36:58.470
And he's a pretty
strong-willed kid.

00:36:58.470 --> 00:37:02.500
And Jack has been mentoring him,
