families, things like that.

00:40:29.570 --> 00:40:33.320
So it's a real message around
if you want your employees to be

00:40:33.320 --> 00:40:36.580
healthy, that it's just not a
nice-to-have, it's a must-have.

00:40:36.580 --> 00:40:37.955
DEAN ORNISH: And
it's unfortunate

00:40:37.955 --> 00:40:40.020
